name: Magic mask episode 1, The end is just the beginning
description: Episode 1 of the magic mask. When the demon lord attacked the human world the humans made a magical weapon in a form of a mask. The strongest mask wielder the "mask king" fought the demon lord. The battle was intense and despite how powerful the mask king is, he is still no match for the demon lord. the demon struck the mask king's chest. In the verge of death he used all of his mana to summon an angel and sacrifice himself in order to seal the demon lord.
